that is the critical thing.

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:53.640
So that's y1, y2 prime
minus y2, y1 prime.

00:06:56.360 --> 00:06:58.090
That's the function.

00:06:58.090 --> 00:06:59.840
Remember we know y1 and y2.

00:06:59.840 --> 00:07:04.560
